overview.en: WellSpring is an integrated information platform strives to become the “Medium” for top-quality blockchain projects all over the world. Project selected by our patent mechanism can benefit from our one-stop services, cover timely update localization, community promotion campaign, target traffic supply, and a built-in crypto exchange with OTC services in WellSpring’s coming version of app.
overview.zh: Wellspring的目标是成为全球优质项目们的第二官网、第二社区，帮项目一站式解决中日韩翻译、社区传播、交易问题，App将会是一个专门面向区块链行业的Medium。
